{"tid":1145779,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ PS4&Xbox One ]《CODE VEIN 噬血代碼》於今日開始開放申請網絡測試資格","createTime":"2019-05-09T00:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T14:34:56.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d33299893b20c31923880ab6d0b500a8760beaf4","tid":1145779,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T00:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYmnfbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYmnfbH.jpg&h=490ab413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《噬血代碼》游戲故事「序章」、據點、角色自定義系統演示公開，遊戲已於今日開始開放申請網絡測試資格，實施時間預定於5月中旬發表，平台為PS4與Xbox One（Xbox One版報名時間另行公布），實施地區包括日本、北美、歐洲以及亞洲。<br />\n<br />\n測試版可以體驗游戲故事「序章」，並能探索深層地圖「祭品之城」。<br />\n<br />\n本作將登陸PS4/Xbox One/PC平台，繁體中文版預定於2019年內發售。<br />\n<br />\n申請頁面：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bandainamcoent.com/landing/code-vein-network-test?fbclid=IwAR0FQ8IKs-UIyyUzZtzCve73Ola5yGjNJxW4KzKxmaEAtZLx-FNPM6EhAgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bandainamcoent.com%2Flanding%2Fcode-vein-network-test%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0FQ8IKs-UIyyUzZtzCve73Ola5yGjNJxW4KzKxmaEAtZLx-FNPM6EhAgc&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=8ed12377\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bandainamcoent.com/landing/code-vein-network-test?fbclid=IwAR0FQ8IKs-UIyyUzZtzCve73Ola5yGjNJxW4KzKxmaEAtZLx-FNPM6EhAgc</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78STp2DMuK4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D78STp2DMuK4&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=9c3b7ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78STp2DMuK4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znWMDoJNAA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DznWMDoJNAA8&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyftT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=03ec2196\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=znWMDoJNAA8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://